The '''Wizard Product Review''' is a fortnightly magic review show started by World Magic Shop in May 2010<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YYT_Z3iE-us&index=184&list=PLNQWkn5llQPoDPPa95WrdbYQjUBAsun-l|title=Wizard Product Review Pilot|last=|first=|date=May 2010|website=youtube.com|publisher=World Magic shop|accessdate=}}</ref> It featured guests such as magician [[Paul Daniels]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ThZehK9oHg|title=Wizard Product Review VIP Guest|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|accessdate=}}</ref> The show brings in a weekly audience of around 10,000 viewers; mostly magicians.
== Hosts == The show was originally hosted by [[David Penn (magician)]] and [[Craig Petty]] until 2015 when Craig was replaced by [[Sean Heydon]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w3-WuP8-3LI|title=Sean Heydon Soccer AM|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|accessdate=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jWedHAvn9jo|title=Wizard Product Review 268|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|accessdate=}}</ref> who continues to host the show to date. Guest hosts have included magicians from all over the world including [http://www.waynefoxmagic.co.uk/ Magician] Wayne Fox<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M5pemdAb3rM|title=Wizard Product Review Wayne Fox|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|accessdate=}}</ref> and [http://www.the-sheffield-magician.com Sheffield Magician] Arron Jones.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MTCHqy2gClc|title=Wizard Product Review Arron Jones|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|accessdate=}}</ref>
